        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（我的名字是肴，二十四岁，居无定所，未婚。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（我的原则是以健康为首要条件。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（虽然是独自一人，自力更生地长大，但不抽烟，没有其他不良嗜好，酒也很少碰，总会往保温水杯里撒一把枸杞。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（每天十一点半准时入睡，睡前会进行例行半小时的瑜伽锻炼。不管当晚有多疲劳，一定会记得仔细护肤，然后才上床休息。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（通常都能如婴儿般酣眠，然后错过闹铃，开始编迟到的理由。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（没有遥不可及的追求，也不会给自己施加过多工作压力。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（我最大的期望就是能过上平静且安稳的人生。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "自我介绍这样差不多就可以了吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "研究员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "等等，别急着溜啊你。还差一道手续呢……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "肴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员不是已经批复过了吗？你说陶董不在的时候找分析员批复就可以了啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "研究员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "现在有新流程，分析员批复过后，还需要监察员的批复，审批才能通过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "肴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "新流程？监察员？哪儿冒出来的？监察谁啊？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "研究员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你说呢……哎，董事会空降过来的，叫姬辰星。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "研究员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从现在开始，这里所有的事情都要过她的手……这是上面的意思，我们就老老实实配合吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "董事会发给您的邮件里应该已经提过了吧？陶董因为……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-2",
        "Flag": "b-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "b-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因身体不适而休假，工作由你和我共同分担。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以，分析员您突然找我还有什么别的事情吗？我眼下还有个会……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-3",
        "Flag": "b-3",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "b-3-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "盯着她的眼睛",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "陶大约在三天前就没有再公开露面。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与此同时，总是捧着纸质书本，名为姬辰星的“监察员”，带着剽悍精干的安全部干员，走进了大楼，甚至直接借用了陶的办公室。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我只是收到了一封董事会署名的邮件，含糊其词地解释了陶的去向。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "26a",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "同时告诉我，我调动安全部的权限已经被取消，由姬辰星接管……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "结合现状，推测便不可避免地滑向了阴谋论一侧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，如果你想询问陶董的去向，我知道的并不比你更多。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "假如你仔细查阅公司的权限变更记录，就会发现……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在五九年的六月五日，五八年的四月二十一日……陶董每年都会进行类似的休假。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不知道这样能否消除你的疑虑，但我确实要去开会了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "军方准备就你们在天楼引发的事故对公司进行问责，分析员，如果你感兴趣，也可以一起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "抱着戏谑玩味的心态，我跟在少女的身后走进了办公室，军方代表比我们更先到达，在这里等待。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你好，我是姬辰星，这位是playername，分析员。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "军方代表",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，二位好，我代表军方来召开这次会议，你们可以称呼我为“零三六”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "军方代表",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "迫于社会舆论的压力，军方希望贵司能够在可控条件下，开放庚号大门，将零区内尚没有受到污染影响的平民放出。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那道门没有打开的可能性，已经错过了最佳时机，军方应该很清楚这点。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "军方代表",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以我方强调，是在可控条件下。或者可以通过别的方案，运送民众……比如通过空运？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从数据分析，泰坦污染没有规律性可言。计划一旦开始就无法停止，如果在空运过程中遭遇污染干扰，出现事故……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这种后果，是我们两方都无法承受的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这样的教训，在二零五七年的十月十八日我们已经领教过一回，当时现场的惨烈状况，贵方那里应该也有一份资料保存。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "军方代表“零三六”顿时哑口无言。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "军方代表",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那么，可以退一步。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "军方代表",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果贵方向我们提供海姆达尔部队有关“激发天启”的实验数据……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们不能提供“激发天启”的实验数据，但可以提供代号<orange>“萨迦”项目</>的全套方案。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "46a",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“萨迦”？我没有听过这个项目的名称。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "贵方想要的制衡与威慑力，通过“萨迦”项目也同样能够实现。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "军方代表",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这个……我没办法自己做出决定。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "军方代表",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我需要询问一下上将。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "军方代表",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们同意这个方案。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "军方代表",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "接下来，“萨迦”如何向我方交付，相关的细则合约是？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的同事卡罗琳会跟您商讨剩余细节。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "非常感谢贵方的谅解，那么会议就到这里吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "53a",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "完全不需要我插手，姬辰星就如同快刀斩乱麻一般，将军方的不合理要求一一应付。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-5",
        "Flag": "b-5",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "b-5-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你等一下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-6",
        "Flag": "b-6",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "b-6-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“萨迦”是什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "姬辰星看着我，完全以公事公办的语气跟我交谈。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，我只是按照事先撰写好的方案进行谈判，充当董事会的传话筒而已。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我相信那位军方代表也和我一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "努力维持着冰块脸的少女一边说着，一边竖起左手的食指，轻轻敲了敲自己的额头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我在这里预演了谈判的所有可能，这算是……我的天赋。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当然，我也预演到了，你对我的“空降”会有所不满。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，我对你个人并没有任何偏见，我希望我们能以理性，而非感性来解决合作上的困难。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "姬辰星向我伸出了手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-7",
        "Flag": "b-7",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "b-7-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说完了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……对，说完了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-8",
        "Flag": "b-8",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "b-8-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说完了就回答问题吧。“萨迦”是什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她勉力在我面前维持着镇静，但被她自己轻轻咬住的下唇却在无意间出卖了她的内心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不想跟一个身为棋子的无辜少女多作什么计较，就眼下的状况而言，她表现得已经很好了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "真正让我觉得恶心的是派她来此的那群董事会的老家伙们——忽然之间来这么一手，是生怕我查不出什么猫腻来么。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
